column2: Court is about food; that's what matters.
Tendency demonstrates with ageing losing counting capability.
The intestine of any creature is indestructible.
An algorithm for automation is symmetrically easy.
Few fish can give birth without breeding.
Compromise freedom to become safe & secure.
Job signatures are granular to formal conversations.
Documentation seeks periodical attention more than self-existence.
The natural aspect decreases but never increases.
Education is about what is already there.
